A tall Western man standing on the ancient stone steps of the Great Wall of China, surrounded by a small group of cheerful Chinese tourists eagerly posing beside him for photos, their cameras and phones raised. The scene is bathed in warm golden afternoon light, with the iconic serpentine wall stretching dramatically into misty mountains behind them. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, gentle pastoral atmosphere, expressive animated faces full of genuine joy and curiosity, delicate cloud wisps drifting across a pale blue sky, autumn foliage in warm oranges and reds dotting the surrounding hillsides.
